Classes in org.cougaar.core.component used by org.cougaar.planning.plugin
Binder
          A Binder is an implementation of a BindingSite: that is an implementation of the Service-like relationship API between a child component and its parent.
BinderBase
          BinderBase contains logic for the parent link (ContainerAPI) but not the child link.
BinderFactory
          A BinderFactory provides Binder instances on behalf of a ContainingComponent or ServiceProvider to wrap Child components.
BinderFactorySupport
          Implement the basics of a BinderFactory.
BinderFactoryWrapper
          An idea for the future: A BinderFactory which encapsulates all BinderFactories known to a component of a lower priority.
BinderWrapper
          A base class for a BinderWrapper: A binder which is interposed between a container and another binder.
BindingSite
          A BindingSite class names and specifies a specific parent Component (Container) to child Component relationship API, e.g. the API of a parent which a child may invoke.
Component
          A Component is the base class of the Component and Service Model.
ContainerAPI
          ContainerAPI is the interface used by Binder and/or BinderFactory to invoke Binder-privileged methods on the parent Container.
DelegatingServiceBroker
          A Simple ServiceBroker which just delegates all queries to another, useful for making restricted extentions.
ExtendedServiceBroker
          A ServiceBroker with extended methods to support the ViewService.
ServiceBroker
          Cougaar component Service Broker.
ServiceFilter
          A BinderFactoryWrapper which wraps components using a Binder which examines and, optionally, modifies, wraps, or audits service requests.
ServiceFilterBinder
          A Wrapper Binder contructed by ServiceFilter which watches service requests and has convenient overridable points where extensions may monitor, edit, veto or wrap services requested by the client.
ServiceFilterBinder.FilteringServiceBroker
          Base class for filtering/auditing/etc services, extending DelegatingServiceBroker for security.
StateObject
          An Object that contains internal state.
SubscriptionLifeCycle
          Hook to start subscriptions as a pseudo life-cycle event
